  Kate looked sensational in the purple gown, which was cut short to show off the actress’ toned legs. The garment featured puffed sleeves with huge frills, with a similar frilled out design on the skirt. The dress also had a plunging V-neck, and a tie around the waist to accentuate Kate’s petite figure. The star accessorised with some purple high heels, a matching clutch and some delicate drop down earrings.   